Download Statement of Operations of the non-financial public sector

get_fiscal.Rd

Download Statement of Operations of the non-financial public sector

Usage

get_fiscal(frecuencia = "Mensual")

Arguments

frecuencia

A character string that specifies the frequency of the exchange rates to be downloaded. Valid options are "Mensual", or "Anual".

Value

a tibble
